            &copy; {year} LideraZap. Todos os direitos reservados.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex justify-center gap-6">
            <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:text-primary transition-colors" aria-label="Instagram">
